1. *Kapetana* su pozdravili svi putnici. (The captain was greeted by all the passengers.)

2. On je postao *kapetan* nakon deset godina. (He became a captain after ten years.)

3. *Kapetan* je poslao poruku preko radija. (The captain sent a message via the radio.)

4. *Kapetanovi* su prijatelji bili veoma impresionirani. (The captain's friends were very impressed.)

5. *Kapetana* je zamolio da obezbedi dodatnu opremu. (The captain was asked to provide additional equipment.)